"     Noreen A Hynes, MD, MPH, DTM&amp;H",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?0/30/490/contributors\">",
"     Robert H Fletcher, MD, MSc",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
